'''Umboo''' was a province on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Roon/Legends|Roon]]. It was home to the [[Yomm family]].

==Behind the scenes==
In earlier drafts of {{Film|I}}, Umboo was identified as the homeworld of [[Wan Sandage/Legends|Wan Sandage]].<ref>[[Star Wars: Episode I Insider's Guide|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''Insider's Guide'']]</ref>

